    "crystal_structure": "Rigid rod-like mesogenic units self-align into liquid-crystalline order in the melt, which is retained (frozen in) on solidification -- giving highly oriented, anisotropic mechanical and thermal expansion properties (notably a high Z-axis, i.e. through-thickness, coefficient of thermal expansion).",
